OL,3,CInquest for child killer Ian Huntley
OL,4,Cto open in County Durham next month
OL,6,FAn inquest is due to open next month
OL,7,Ffor Soham killer Ian Huntley who died
OL,8,Fdays after a prison attack.
OL,10,FThe 52-year-old died in the Royal
OL,11,FVictoria Infirmary in Newcastle on 7
OL,12,FMarch after he was allegedly attacked
OL,13,Fwith a metal bar in a workshop at HMP
OL,14,FFrankland in Durham on 26 February.
OL,16,FThe County Durham and Darlington
OL,17,FCoroner has posted details of an
OL,18,Finquest opening hearing, due to be
OL,19,Fheld in Crook, County Durham, on 14
OL,20,FApril.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
