OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774617128
OL,3,CInquest for child killer Ian Huntley
OL,4,Cto open in County Durham next month
OL,6,FListed under the name Ian Kevin
OL,7,FHuntley, the inquest opening will be
OL,8,Fheard by senior coroner Jeremy
OL,9,FChipperfield.
OL,11,FIt has been reported there will be no
OL,12,Ffuneral service for the child killer
OL,13,Fand The Sun has said it understood
OL,14,FHuntley's family will scatter his
OL,15,Fashes in secret.
OL,17,FAnthony Russell, 43, has been charged
OL,18,Fwith murdering Huntley at the maximum
OL,19,Fsecurity jail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
