OL,3,CInquest for child killer Ian Huntley
OL,4,Cto open in County Durham next month
OL,6,FHe will attend Newcastle Crown Court
OL,7,Fon 24 April for a pre-trial
OL,8,Fpreparation hearing.
OL,10,FHuntley was serving a life sentence
OL,11,Ffor the 2002 murders of 10-year-olds
OL,12,FHolly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,14,FThe ex-school caretaker killed the
OL,15,Fbest friends after they left a family
OL,16,Fbarbecue to buy sweets in Soham,
OL,17,FCambridgeshire, on 4 August 2002. He
OL,18,Fdumped their bodies in a ditch 10
OL,19,Fmiles away.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
