PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774617128
OL,3,CInquest for child killer Ian Huntley
OL,4,Cto open in County Durham next month
OL,6,FThey were not found for 13 days,
OL,7,Fdespite a search involving hundreds of
OL,8,Fpolice.
OL,10,FAt the time, Huntley lived with Maxine
OL,11,FCarr, who was a teaching assistant at
OL,12,FHolly and Jessica's primary school.
OL,14,FHe denied murdering the girls but was
OL,15,Fconvicted after a trial at the Old
OL,16,FBailey in 2003. He was jailed for life
OL,17,Fwith a recommended minimum term of 40
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
