OL,3,CInquest for child killer Ian Huntley
OL,4,Cto open in County Durham next month
OL,6,FCarr gave Huntley a false alibi and
OL,7,Fwas jailed for 21 months for
OL,8,Fperverting the course of justice. She
OL,9,Fis now living under a new identity.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
